node.text: It’s no surprise that my work is way more tolerable when it’s balanced with adventures and good people! That being said, where should I fish next?!? #nurselife #bucketlistadventures

node.text:
Fish in one hand, estrogen in the other, see which one fills up first 😭😂😝
⠀
Seriously though, these ladies are dime pieces! And so are the fish! I love making friends with other like-minded female anglers and traveling to new places to explore and fish 🎣💃🏽 A special thanks to @rentadventurenow for putting us on some beasts! And to @tworiversinn for posting us up in comfy beds and with the best hospitality you can find in Thermopolis 🙏🐟
⠀
⠀
#girlswhoflyfish #flyfishing #fishe #womenonthefly #wyoming
⠀#browntroutflyfishing 
⠀

node.text:
Happy Wednesday, errrrrbody!!
⠀
I thought it would be fun to start something new! On hump days, I’m going to ask y’all random questions (that I sometimes ask myself 🤣)
⠀
Soooo, would you rather travel through time or fly like Superman?
⠀
⠀
**Featuring the new Grey’s Anatomy Spandex Stretch Antimicrobial scrubs!!
⠀
#happyhumpday #nursetalk #wouldyouratherwednesday #scrublife

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Kerrie | APRN, FNP-C, CMRN on June 15, 2021 tagging @shadyrays, and @scrubsandbeyond. May be an image of 1 person, jewelry and eyeglasses.

node.text:
The truth is, we all want to be better. Whether with our health, our relationships, our mentality, our careers, our fishing skills 😝…It’s in our human nature to desire more growth, more internal peace, more flexibility, more acceptance of each others’ differences, and to ultimately become the best versions of ourselves. There’s always room for improvement, but don’t be too hard on yourself 💓 #selflove #nursetalk
⠀

node.text:
Can we all agree it feels refreshing and oddly privileged to get off work and head into Home Depot without putting on a mask?!? 🤡 #suckitcorona #economybounceback
⠀
Even with this shift in the pandemic, please keep washing your hands and covering your mouth when you cough or sneeze! And stay home if you have a fever! #nursetalk #scrublife #stayhealthy 
⠀
@koihappiness
Also. How about these scrubs! Wearing: Koi lite stretch top and pant, Action V-Neck and Power Jogger Pants in Heather Charcoal 💕

Hold em high, look em in the eye, and tell em that you love em!!! And check out Colleen with her PB #smallmouth at 4.8 pounds!! #sisterswhofish 
⠀
Great day with @shawnrogers_denverbassguide
⠀
⠀
#fishkissfriday #raiseyourbass #smallmouthbass

node.text:
🤠✨BOOTS  GIVEAWAY✨🤠
⠀
I am excited to be partnering with @alviesboots today for this BIG giveaway of a pair of leather cowhide boots.
⠀
@alviesboots is a brand based in Austin, TX, that makes insanely comfortable cowboy boots and flip flops.
⠀
Follow these steps to enter:
1️⃣ Follow @alviesboots and @nurse_kerrie 
2️⃣ Like this post
3️⃣ Tag a friend in the comments.
Each comment is a separate entry. Enter by May 29th at midnight mountain time.
⠀
⠀
➡️ The giveaway will close on May 29th and the winner will be announced within 48 hours via Instagram story. The winner will be able to choose any choice of flops but will be limited to Alvies' cowhide leather boots only. Good luck to all, and thank you for entering!
⠀
⠀
This giveaway is not affiliated with Instagram.
⠀
#cowboyboots #alvies #giveaway
